namespace Advent2018;

public partial class Day13 : Advent.Day
{
    /*
        *  Description -   Input is a set of lines defining the layout of train tracks and the current locations and directions of the carts on them.
        *                  Carts move in turn top to bottom one step at a time.  On reaching intersections, a cart turns left first time, straight ahead the second,
        *                  right the third and so on.
        *  
        *  Part 1 -        What is the location of the first crash to happen?
        *  Part 2 -        Removing both carts involved in a crash, what is the location of the last one left unscathed?
